Hi @everyone 

I must confess that I personally really don't like all the characters in P&R and I really hoped must of you go with option A, but the people has spoken and I will implement this feature.
BUT it will be an **optional** for those who choose to play with political simulation.

So you will choose when starting a new game if politics will be handled in micro (option B) or macro (option A)

Love you all ♥

Many of the Alpha testers are currently feeling frustrated with the lack of micromanagement regarding politics.
So I would love the hear everyone opinion on this matter.

What would you want to see more ?

🇦 Abstract way to increase support with parties through political influence score (if you gained enough score you can increase support with parties)

🇧 Head of parties characters (not real) that you will need to interact with to increase support (promises, meetings, etc.)
